Note that the parabola $y^2 = 4x$ opens to the right.  Let $2t$ be the $y$-coordinate of $B.$  Then
\[x = \frac{y^2}{4} = \frac{(2t)^2}{4} = t^2,\]so $B = (t^2,2t).$

